        "background_color": "none",
        "heading": "<h2>A mist to refresh skin prone to breakouts, redness and sensitivity</h2>",
        "text": "<p>Powered by hypochlorous acid (HOCl), Dermal Mist helps calm the look and feel of stressed skin and support a fresh, balanced complexion—without irritation.<br/></p><p>Perfect for skin that experiences <em>breakouts, visible redness, or post-treatment sensitivity</em>, this lightweight mist helps soothe the look of skin and protect against everyday environmental stressors.<br/></p><p>It’s fragrance-free, non-drying, and gentle enough to use anytime, anywhere, even over makeup.</p>",
        "button_label": "SHOP NOW",
